{"tid":2070761,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英國駐華使館稱中英聯合聲明至今仍然有效","createTime":"2020-06-19T10:43:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T12:09:02.000Z","uid":5195,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"cca1bead8d3bb943ddf5891baa7830d43ed3a666","tid":2070761,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T10:43:04.000Z","msg":"英國駐華使館在微信公眾號，反駁中方近期就涉港問題的一些說法。<br />\n<br />\n對於有指《中英聯合聲明》是歷史文件，不具備現實意義。使館回應說，聲明是在聯合國登記在案的有法律效力國際條約，至今仍然有效，協議明確香港的高度自治權，除了外交與防禦等事項，香港享有的權利自由50年不變。<br />\n<br />\n使館說，英國明確承認香港是中國一部分，為了維護世界和平安全，每個國家都應該尊重並支持國際法，港區國安法違背《中英聯合聲明》中，中國對國際社會的責任，有進一步分裂香港脆弱社會體系的風險，因此英方與其他國家一同敦促中國重新考慮，為回歸和平和諧努力。"},{"pid":"781a3032b07eedc8f87abb55ccc3a73d421451a1","tid":2070761,"uid":31215,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T10:46:03.000Z","msg":"改bno嗰時就有效<br />\n反國安法嗰時就冇效<br />\n輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ce57fa532f43c8a74f5f0a392d0b4fd94eb2bc","tid":2070761,"uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T10:48:10.000Z","msg":"我重點去左「在微信公眾號」<br />\n真係好勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a97149570e71b33ee085a16832c9a454deec2a14","tid":2070761,"uid":8776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70ce57fa532f43c8a74f5f0a392d0b4fd94eb2bc","tid":2070761,"uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T10:48:10.000Z","msg":"我重點去左「在微信公眾號」<br />\n真係好勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T10:50:42.000Z","msg":"會唔會俾人ban?"},{"pid":"56d652466598e23308b7c8e1536dd3619e0bdd76","tid":2070761,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T10:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets